<TEXT>
   Chancellor Helmut Kohl has acknowledged
what his government long denied _ West German companies may have
helped build and supply a Libyan plant that U.S. officials believe
is on the verge of full-scale production of poison gas.
   Kohl said in a television appearance late Thursday that
authorities have uncovered new documents implicating West German
