   Judge Henry A. Politz announced the decision Thursday for the
three-judge 5th U.S. Circuit Court of Appeals panel.
   Guy M. Struve, an attorney for Church's, said he was disappointed
and did not know when the chain would decide whether to appeal the
ruling.
