<HEAD>London Stock Prices Stronger At Midday</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: will be led after closing</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices strengthened at midday Friday, led
higher by a burst of institutional buying.
   The market also was cheered on by the strong trend in Tokyo
earlier Friday and in New York on Thursday, traders said.
   Dealers said there were patches of active trading at midmorning,
with some large institutions snapping up some shares they considered
to be bargains.
