Street Journal article described the company as a takeover candidate.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks rose
.42 to 159.68. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up .45 at 315.45.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 92.49 million shares with two
hours to go.
